    "description": "《机甲工程师》是机甲爱好者的理想游戏。在这里你可以看到机甲作战的各个方面，从优化反应炉到调试武器系统。你需要精心调整和平衡每台机甲的重量、能量和散热系统，让它们的作战效率达到最高。<br><br>驾驶员技术和情绪、基地和资源的管理效率也有重要影响。你需要将精心调试的机甲投入任务，在半自动战斗（可暂停）中进行决策，对抗外星异种大军，决定人类的命运。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一，开始组装机甲</h2>从反应炉开始，选择活塞和喷嘴，提高其能量输出，再加入辅助模块，控制核心温度。你要考虑各种因素，包括部署环境的温度，过热会导致机甲在战斗中停机，这可不是什么好事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/3227142ff3c79b6ce6964282a5a8624a.poster.avif?t=1759166363\" width=462 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/3227142ff3c79b6ce6964282a5a8624a.webm?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/3227142ff3c79b6ce6964282a5a8624a.mp4?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第二，准备武器</h2>自定义你的武器并在模拟器中测试，武器属性有射速、重量、能耗、精度和火力。你需要考虑可能遭遇的敌人和弹药消耗的速度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/d201a40c71b4fbfff6ff10cfb0b63faf.poster.avif?t=1759166363\" width=464 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/d201a40c71b4fbfff6ff10cfb0b63faf.webm?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/d201a40c71b4fbfff6ff10cfb0b63faf.mp4?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第三，完成机甲</h2>载重和可用能量也是机甲的两大关键属性。制定你的战略，根据地形和敌人进行取舍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b04b634847ee36a2ce9e82f97b0c07c1.poster.avif?t=1759166363\" width=464 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b04b634847ee36a2ce9e82f97b0c07c1.webm?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b04b634847ee36a2ce9e82f97b0c07c1.mp4?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第四，选择驾驶员</h2>如果驾驶员经验不足或没有得到足够的休息，即使是最强的机甲也有可能表现不佳，压力和虫群一样令人厌烦。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/7a6c5b9215a0e53a84180ae51ff25a66.poster.avif?t=1759166363\" width=410 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/7a6c5b9215a0e53a84180ae51ff25a66.webm?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/7a6c5b9215a0e53a84180ae51ff25a66.mp4?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第五，战斗时间！</h2>给你勇敢的驾驶员一个位置或进攻命令，看他们全力求生，完成任务。探索世界的废墟，避开敌人基地和危险的怪物，找到所有的太空船部件并逃离地球。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b64934b94466580c4e20fa9020f38ccb.poster.avif?t=1759166363\" width=420 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b64934b94466580c4e20fa9020f38ccb.webm?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428520/extras/b64934b94466580c4e20fa9020f38ccb.mp4?t=1759166363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
